room_title: Escape room "Special Inquiry" by That Escape Room in San Francisco
room_description: Sheriffs are pretty sure Terry Edward is the murderer of the recent teenager missing case, but they don't have any proof. You guys are the FBI's top investigation team. Your job is to find the corpse he killed and get some evidence from his house. He's out for a meeting for an hour. Get out of there before he gets back.
